00:03:02,910 --> 00:03:04,950
Qui veut des palourdes fraîches ?

43
00:03:05,950 --> 00:03:07,750
Laissez passer !

44
00:03:11,620 --> 00:03:13,100
Entrez, entrez !

45
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,800
Venez goûter
nos célèbres nouilles-fleurs !

46
00:03:58,210 --> 00:04:00,210
Toi, là !

47
00:04:00,470 --> 00:04:02,090
Le nouveau !

48
00:04:02,510 --> 00:04:06,220
C'est toi qui as fait ça ?

49
00:04:06,700 --> 00:04:09,310
Ouais, boss.

50
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:11,270
Y a un souci ?

51
00:04:11,730 --> 00:04:15,230
"Y a un souci ?" qu'il demande,
ce bougre d'âne !

52
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:17,570
C'est juste parfait.

53
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,730
J'te félicite.

54
00:04:21,290 --> 00:04:23,520
Grand dadais !

55
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:26,410
Bien sûr que c'est nickel !

56
00:04:26,700 --> 00:04:28,280
Jouez votre rôle !

57
00:04:33,460 --> 00:04:34,370
Oh...

58
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:38,840
Ah d'accord... Merci !

59
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:42,330
Enfoiré !

